Read `AGENTS.md` and `docs/snapshot-v0.17.0.md` before implementation.

Rules:
- Mutations go through command handlers only.
- Outbound events originate from `outbox_events` only.
- PostgreSQL is the Phase 0 command/control/outbox/projection plane.
- TigerBeetle, pgvector, DuckDB, broker/CDC, external connector runtime, and full tiled workspace are post-MVP/evidence-gated.
- Run `bash scripts/validate-pack.sh` before handoff.
